overview: The user wanted to significantly improve the aesthetic appeal of their
  sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too generic. The
  assistant undertook a comprehensive review of the app's existing styling, from
  global CSS to individual UI components and sections. The approach involved
  introducing a new, calming sleep-themed color palette, incorporating subtle
  background elements, and redesigning core components like the progress bar,
  cards, and form fields. Key decisions included using deeper indigo/purple
  tones with teal accents, enhancing visual hierarchy in the intro section, and
  refining the appearance of interactive elements like checkboxes, radio
  buttons, and sliders. The outcome is a more sophisticated, professional, and
  visually engaging application that better reflects its purpose as a sleep
  health assessment tool.
